<br>
Yes the ozone layer is melting, degrading whatever.. and the icecaps are melting, but when will people take it seriously. As for the major floods we had last year I spoke to a really old lady not so long about it, and she said that they &quot;we've always had floods, but we never had news until recently.. so not many people remember them!&quot;<br>
